	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've taken an interest in these oddball pre-Famicom consoles, and I was wondering if there is any contemporary (or past) homebrew/amateur programming for these systems? Flash carts? Technical documentation? Google is coming up empty.<br /><br />And what is the equivalent term for 'homebrew' in Japanese?

		

		</td>
